Shoot'O'Chenko: THE NEW INCREDIBLE Op. Wolf Clone from FP!

The game is basically an Operation Wolf clone, your aim is
to throw shit to Petro.LHA and other valuable targets.
The game will feature deformed graphic (a la Day Of the Tentacle),
high quality speech during game, powerups and so on
Screenshots will be uploaded to Aminet soon, then we will
release a rolling demo. A final version is expected to be
released at Planet Amiga show in Italy.





